{"tid":123764,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[柒黑警] 好心d阿叔阿嬸就收皮唔好講時事啦","createTime":"2017-02-17T05:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T03:35:07.000Z","uid":23815,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4429b790ee2dd7587263bd2a0f5b2fc0f8fadbd8","tid":123764,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T05:19:41.000Z","msg":"岩先落街下茶記食野<br />\n佢地d侍應阿嬸一見到柒警罪成就話曾健超都應該要比人拉 要坐監<br />\n我食住個飯差d噴撚哂出黎<br />\n明明人地兩星期唔夠就罪成坐撚左五星期<br />\n唔講我仲以為曾健超無事無幹行開左<br />\n<br />\n一味話柒黑係衰低能 係呢d公方行私刑<br />\n又話曾健超抵死 要拉<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 你唔係留意開呢d野就唔好衝出黎柒啦<br />\n黃絲又點 ? 今次單野斷正 你仲夠膽講人地誤判 ?<br />\n當面屌鳩你地又話d後生既唔識野<br />\n唔當面屌柒你又以為自己新聞觸覺好高<br />\n<br />\n港豬真係當之無愧"},{"pid":"7769ef3f6bd5fc87359fe0351b228d98d4196ec9","tid":123764,"uid":1900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:22:44.000Z","msg":"其實依家D人根本就唔會理警察有冇知法犯法<br />\n佢地只係知道曾健超抵打  <br />\n因為佢抵打  所以果7個警察就冇錯到<br />\n<br />\n你問返佢地如果打既唔係任何佔中人仕<br />\n而係一個普通人  佢地就會冇聲出<br />\n然後會好大聱咁講佢地唔會打普通人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依班人根本就係對人唔係對事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79391e1356a3e83ae2cd5241d7a40b9b4a8769b2","tid":123764,"uid":1900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:26:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實依家D人根本就唔會理警察有冇知法犯法<br />\n佢地只係知道曾健超抵打  <br />\n因為佢抵打  所以果7個警察就冇錯到<br />\n<br />\n你問返佢地如果打既唔係任何佔中人仕<br />\n而係一個普通人  佢地就會冇聲出<br />\n然後會好大聱咁講佢地唔會打普通人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依班人根本就係對人唔係對事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後又會屌 佔中 年初2事件  點解比人拉人左既判咁輕<br />\n佢地7個就判咁重<br />\n班友完全唔明  香港既法律上 舉證係由控方付責  <br />\n律政師自己唔夠證證據告人就梗係判得輕"},{"pid":"0d71a8d45d42d170a052a1bbd96cdb36b6ace056","tid":123764,"uid":56833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:27:55.000Z","msg":"算啦 班廢中就係咁架啦 輸打贏要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cda647df4fcec1286881533b17661eb4adeef82","tid":123764,"uid":52936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"有班是非不分既廢老 真係好可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912299ccf4e2e7b2a0316a94c71bf17bc88f1b19","tid":123764,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T01:21:57.000Z","msg":"以為你講毓民&hellip;"},{"pid":"00d4504e7ab61d03f729cf2a1e19cfdd3d46acdf","tid":123764,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T01:36:24.000Z","msg":"啲低級黑警又係呢啲心態<br />\n<br />\n大佬啊 唔講政治<br />\n<br />\n七個鎖住一個打<br />\n<br />\n一定犯法架啦<br />\n<br />\n七個平民打一個都犯法啦<br />\n<br />\n警察就唔犯法咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4bcd23db554479b8a62c30c572554ea28c9278","tid":123764,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T01:38:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實依家D人根本就唔會理警察有冇知法犯法<br />\n佢地只係知道曾健超抵打  <br />\n因為佢抵打  所以果7個警察就冇錯到<br />\n<br />\n你問返佢地如果打既唔係任何佔中人仕<br />\n而係一個普通人  佢地就會冇聲出<br />\n然後會好大聱咁講佢地唔會打普通人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依班人根本就係對人唔係對事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /